# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REPO POLICY — this is the PUBLIC protocol repo. It contains ONLY:
#   (1) the protocol itself — spec, formal model, conformance vectors, packages, docs; and
#   (2) DEPERSONALIZED, operator-facing material (generic operator tasks/tooling).
# Everything else — personal AI-agent config, private task trackers, internal research,
# red-team notes, commercial/operator strategy — is gitignored and NEVER committed here.
# When in doubt: if it isn't protocol or depersonalized-operator, it does not belong in git.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# secrets — NEVER committed (holds the diary signing key, among others)
.env
.env.*

# dependencies
node_modules/
packages/*/node_modules/
package-lock.json

# private — personal AI-agent config + instructions (not protocol; never public)
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
.claude/
.agents/

# private — operator toolkit (never published, not part of the public standard)
packages/ustate/
packages/ust-mcp/conformance.mjs
packages/ust-mcp/demo-all.mjs
packages/ust-mcp/demo-mcp-ladder.mjs

# private — internal research / red-team / spec drafts
rnd/
INTERNAL-*

# private — local beads task db (never leak a private tracker into the public protocol repo)
.beads/

# os
.DS_Store

# Beads / Dolt files (added by bd init)
.dolt/
*.db
.beads-credential-key
.beads/proxieddb/
